{"type":"message","id":"f126ca60","parentId":"898f6c90","timestamp":"2026-02-27T00:31:38.652Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到大文件了！\n1. `/var/log/ludo-game.log` - 1.9G\n2. `/var/log/ludo-room.log` - 841M\n3. `/var/log/ludo-room.error.log` - 668M\n4. `/var/log/journal` - 2.1G\n\nludo 相关的日志文件占用约 3.4G！这是主要的磁盘占用来源。\n\n现在我要执行改进措施：\n\n**C. 生成修复脚本**\n1. 创建系统日志清理脚本（清理 ludo 日志 + journalctl）\n2. 创建 Swap 配置脚本\n\n**D. 更新进化历史**\n- 记录新发现的 Pattern（PAT-034、PAT-035）\n- 更新健康评分\n\n让我开始：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## Phase 3: 主动改进\n\n发现主要问题：系统日志占用大量空间（ludo 游戏日志 3.4G）。开始修复：\n\n### C. 生成系统日志清理脚本"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e3ec669599fc447588ac4228","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-log-cleanup.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# system-log-cleanup.sh - 系统日志清理脚本\n# 创建时间: 2026-02-27 08:30 (Round 247)\n# 用途: 清理系统日志释放磁盘空间\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\n# 颜色定义\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nBLUE='\\033[0;34m'\nNC='\\033[0m'\n\n# 日志函数\nlog() {\n  echo -e \"${BLUE}[$(date '+%H:%M:%S')]${NC} $1\"\n}\n\nlog_success() {\n  echo -e \"${GREEN}✅ $1${NC}\"\n}\n\nlog_warning() {\n  echo -e \"${YELLOW}⚠️  $1${NC}\"\n}\n\nlog_error() {\n  echo -e \"${RED}❌ $1${NC}\"\n}\n\n# 获取当前磁盘使用率\nget_disk_usage() {\n  df -h / | awk 'NR==2 {print $5}' | tr -d '%'\n}\n\n# 获取可用空间（GB）\nget_available_space() {\n  df -h / | awk 'NR==2 {print $4}' | sed 's/G//'\n}\n\necho \"=========================================\"\necho \"🧹 系统日志清理工具\"\necho \"时间: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\"\necho \"=========================================\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 初始状态\nINITIAL_USAGE=$(get_disk_usage)\nINITIAL_SPACE=$(get_available_space)\n\nlog \"初始磁盘使用率: ${INITIAL_USAGE}%\"\nlog \"初始可用空间: ${INITIAL_SPACE}G\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 清理项目\nFREED_SPACE=0\n\n### 1. 清理 Ludo 游戏日志\nlog \"检查 Ludo 游戏日志...\"\n\nLUDO_LOGS=(\n  \"/var/log/ludo-game.log\"\n  \"/var/log/ludo-room.log\"\n  \"/var/log/ludo-room.error.log\"\n)\n\nfor log_file in \"${LUDO_LOGS[@]}\"; do\n  if [[ -f \"$log_file\" ]]; then\n    SIZE=$(du -m \"$log_file\" | awk '{print $1}')\n    log \"  发现 $log_file (${SIZE}MB)\"\n    \n    # 备份最后 1000 行\n    if [[ $SIZE -gt 100 ]]; then\n      BACKUP=\"/var/log/$(basename $log_file).backup-$(date +%Y%m%d)\"\n      tail -1000 \"$log_file\" > \"$BACKUP\" 2>/dev/null || true\n      log \"  已备份最后 1000 行到 $BACKUP\"\n    fi\n    \n    # 清空文件\n    > \"$log_file\"\n    log_success \"已清空 $log_file (释放 ~${SIZE}MB)\"\n    FREED_SPACE=$((FREED_SPACE + SIZE))\n  fi\ndone\n\necho \"\"\n\n### 2. 清理 Journalctl 日志\nlog \"检查 Journalctl 日志...\"\n\nJOURNAL_SIZE=$(journalctl --disk-usage 2>/dev/null | grep -oP '\\d+\\.\\d+G' | head -1 || echo \"0G\")\nlog \"  当前占用: $JOURNAL_SIZE\"\n\nif [[ \"$JOURNAL_SIZE\" != \"0G\" ]]; then\n  # 限制日志大小为 500M\n  journalctl --vacuum-size=500M 2>/dev/null || log_warning \"需要 root 权限清理 journalctl\"\n  log_success \"Journalctl 日志已限制为 500M\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\n\n### 3. 清理旧系统日志\nlog \"检查旧系统日志...\"\n\n# 清理超过 30 天的日志\nOLD_LOGS=$(find /var/log -type f -name \"*.log\" -mtime +30 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\nif [[ $OLD_LOGS -gt 0 ]]; then\n  log \"  发现 $OLD_LOGS 个超过 30 天的日志文件\"\n  \n  # 压缩而非删除\n  find /var/log -type f -name \"*.log\" -mtime +30 -exec gzip {} \\; 2>/dev/null || true\n  log_success \"已压缩 $OLD_LOGS 个旧日志文件\"\nelse\n  log \"  无需清理\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\n\n### 4. 清理 Nginx 旧日志\nlog \"检查 Nginx 旧日志...\"\n\nif [[ -d \"/var/log/nginx\" ]]; then\n  NGINX_OLD=$(find /var/log/nginx -type f -name \"*.gz\" -mtime +30 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n  if [[ $NGINX_OLD -gt 0 ]]; then\n    find /var/log/nginx -type f -name \"*.gz\" -mtime +30 -delete 2>/dev/null || true\n    log_success \"已删除 $NGINX_OLD 个超过 30 天的 Nginx 压缩日志\"\n  else\n    log \"  无需清理\"\n  fi\nfi\n\necho \"\"\n\n### 5. 清理 OpenClaw Session 日志\nlog \"检查 OpenClaw Session 日志...\"\n\nSESSION_DIR=\"/root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions\"\nif [[ -d \"$SESSION_DIR\" ]]; then\n  SESSION_COUNT=$(find \"$SESSION_DIR\" -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n  SESSION_SIZE=$(du -sm \"$SESSION_DIR\" 2>/dev/null | awk '{print $1}')\n  \n  log \"  Session 文件数: $SESSION_COUNT\"\n  log \"  总大小: ${SESSION_SIZE}MB\"\n  \n  # 清理超过 7 天的 session 日志\n  OLD_SESSIONS=$(find \"$SESSION_DIR\" -name \"*.jsonl\" -mtime +7 -type f 2>/dev/null | wc -l)\n  if [[ $OLD_SESSIONS -gt 0 ]]; then\n    find \"$SESSION_DIR\" -name \"*.jsonl\" -mtime +7 -type f -delete 2>/dev/null || true\n    log_success \"已删除 $OLD_SESSIONS 个超过 7 天的 session 日志\"\n  else\n    log \"  无需清理（已在 Round 245 清理）\"\n  fi\nfi\n\necho \"\"\n\n### 最终状态\nFINAL_USAGE=$(get_disk_usage)\nFINAL_SPACE=$(get_available_space)\n\necho \"=========================================\"\necho \"📊 清理结果\"\necho \"=========================================\"\necho \"\"\necho \"磁盘使用率: ${INITIAL_USAGE}% → ${FINAL_USAGE}%\"\necho \"可用空间: ${INITIAL_SPACE}G → ${FINAL_SPACE}G\"\necho \"\"\n\nif [[ ${FINAL_USAGE} -lt ${INITIAL_USAGE} ]]; then\n  IMPROVEMENT=$((INITIAL_USAGE - FINAL_USAGE))\n  log_success \"磁盘使用率降低 ${IMPROVEMENT}%\"\n  log_success \"预计释放空间: ~${FREED_SPACE}MB\"\nelse\n  log \"磁盘使用率保持稳定\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\n\n# 健康评分\nif [[ ${FINAL_USAGE} -lt 70 ]]; then\n  log_success \"磁盘状态: 健康 (< 70%)\"\nelif [[ ${FINAL_USAGE} -lt 85 ]]; then\n  log_warning \"磁盘状态: 正常 (70-85%)\"\nelse\n  log_error \"磁盘状态: 警告 (> 85%) - 建议进一步清理\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=========================================\"\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aeb26ddf1a5f4aa5ae3f6d6b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-log-cleanup.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":556,"output":1861,"cacheRead":49984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52401,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772152251078}}
