{"type":"message","id":"b879c85e","parentId":"0d5784e1","timestamp":"2026-02-27T04:33:56.097Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"评分算法有问题，快速模式下日志和维护模块没有检查，评分是0，导致总分很低。我需要调整算法，让快速模式只计算检查过的模块。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_73047a38a9ed4e8fb3e1d972","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh","oldText":"### 计算总分\ncalculate_total() {\n  # 加权平均\n  TOTAL_SCORE=$(echo \"scale=1; ($RESOURCE_SCORE * 0.3 + $API_SCORE * 0.3 + $LOG_SCORE * 0.2 + $MAINTENANCE_SCORE * 0.2)\" | bc)\n\n  # 限制范围\n  if (( $(echo \"$TOTAL_SCORE > 10\" | bc -l) )); then\n    TOTAL_SCORE=10\n  elif (( $(echo \"$TOTAL_SCORE < 0\" | bc -l) )); then\n    TOTAL_SCORE=0\n  fi\n}","newText":"### 计算总分\ncalculate_total() {\n  # 根据模式调整权重\n  if [[ \"$MODE\" == \"--quick\" ]]; then\n    # 快速模式：只计算资源和 API\n    TOTAL_SCORE=$(echo \"scale=1; ($RESOURCE_SCORE * 0.5 + $API_SCORE * 0.5)\" | bc)\n  else\n    # 完整模式：加权平均\n    TOTAL_SCORE=$(echo \"scale=1; ($RESOURCE_SCORE * 0.3 + $API_SCORE * 0.3 + $LOG_SCORE * 0.2 + $MAINTENANCE_SCORE * 0.2)\" | bc)\n  fi\n\n  # 限制范围\n  if (( $(echo \"$TOTAL_SCORE > 10\" | bc -l) )); then\n    TOTAL_SCORE=10\n  elif (( $(echo \"$TOTAL_SCORE < 0\" | bc -l) )); then\n    TOTAL_SCORE=0\n  fi\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":511,"output":406,"cacheRead":74368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772166822528}}
