     Round 248: 健康编排器 ✨\n```\n\n## 🎯 Skills 统计\n\n- **总 Skills 数**: 23 个 (+1)\n- **新增**: system-health-orchestrator\n- **Pattern 解决率**: 78%\n\n## 🚀 后续行动\n\n### 立即可用\n\n```bash\n# 运行健康检查\n/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh --full\n```\n\n### 建议配置（可选）\n\n```json\n{\n  \"jobId\": \"system-health-quick\",\n  \"schedule\": \"0 * * * * *\",\n  \"command\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh --quick\"\n}\n```\n\n## 📅 下次进化\n\n**时间**: 2026-02-27 16:00 PM\n**重点**: 监控健康检查使用效果、持续优化\n\n---\n\n**进化报告**: `/memory/evolution-2026-02-27-1230.md`\n**Round 记录**: `/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-248-20260227-1230/summary.md`\n**健康检查**: `/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh`\n**Skill 文档**: `/skills/system-health-orchestrator/SKILL.md`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":769,"output":1103,"cacheRead":81088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82960,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772167005608}}
