{"type":"message","id":"60faabf4","parentId":"4f32cbd5","timestamp":"2026-02-27T08:32:48.773Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！Gateway 内存监控脚本现在正常工作了。Gateway 内存使用 1310MB，处于警告状态。现在让我：1. 更新 pattern-registry\n2. 生成进化报告\n3. 提交更改\n\n我还应该更新 health-check.sh 脚本，将 Gateway 检查集成进去。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"### B. 改进现有 Skill - 更新系统健康检查脚本"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_155dd076acdd4eff809309c3","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh","oldText":"  # Swap 检查\n  SWAP_TOTAL=$(free -m | awk '/Swap:/ {print $2}')\n\n  log \"  Swap 配置: ${SWAP_TOTAL}MB\"\n\n  if [[ $SWAP_TOTAL -eq 0 ]]; then\n    log_warning \"未配置 Swap - 建议配置 2GB\"\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 1))\n  else\n    log_info \"Swap 已配置\"\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 2))\n  fi\n\n  # 计算资源评分 (满分 10)\n  RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE * 10 / 20))\n  log \"  资源模块评分: ${RESOURCE_SCORE}/10\"\n  echo \"\"\n}","newText":"  # Swap 检查\n  SWAP_TOTAL=$(free -m | awk '/Swap:/ {print $2}')\n\n  log \"  Swap 配置: ${SWAP_TOTAL}MB\"\n\n  if [[ $SWAP_TOTAL -eq 0 ]]; then\n    log_warning \"未配置 Swap - 建议配置 2GB\"\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 1))\n  else\n    log_info \"Swap 已配置\"\n    RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 2))\n  fi\n\n  # Gateway 内存检查 (Round 249 新增)\n  if [[ -f \"$SCRIPT_DIR/gateway-memory-monitor.sh\" ]]; then\n    GATEWAY_MEM=$(ps aux | grep \"openclaw-gateway\" | grep -v grep | awk '{print int($6/1024)}')\n    if [[ -n \"$GATEWAY_MEM\" ]]; then\n      log \"  Gateway 内存: ${GATEWAY_MEM}MB\"\n\n      if [[ $GATEWAY_MEM -gt 1500 ]]; then\n        log_error \"Gateway 内存: 危险 (> 1500MB)\"\n        RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 2))\n      elif [[ $GATEWAY_MEM -gt 1200 ]]; then\n        log_warning \"Gateway 内存: 警告 (> 1200MB)\"\n        RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE - 1))\n      else\n        log_success \"Gateway 内存: 正常\"\n        RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE + 1))\n      fi\n    fi\n  fi\n\n  # 计算资源评分 (满分 10)\n  RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE * 10 / 20))\n  RESOURCE_SCORE=$((RESOURCE_SCORE > 10 ? 10 : RESOURCE_SCORE))\n  log \"  资源模块评分: ${RESOURCE_SCORE}/10\"\n  echo \"\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":964,"output":650,"cacheRead":97664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99278,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772181144473}}
