{"type":"message","id":"768ef76e","parentId":"b89e44dd","timestamp":"2026-02-27T12:31:30.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"严重问题！日志分析报告显示：\n\n1. **PAT-038**: Gateway 内存泄漏 - 极高风险\n   - 当前: 1840MB (50.1%)\n   - 增长率: 175MB/小时\n   - 系统可用内存: 164MB (危险低)\n   - 健康评分: 5.0/10 (危险)\n\n2. **PAT-039**: 系统内存紧张\n   - 可用: 164MB / 371MB available\n   - 无 Swap\n\n这是紧急情况！需要立即行动：\n1. 配置 Swap（优先）\n2. 监控 Gateway 内存\n3. 考虑重启 Gateway\n\n让我立即创建紧急响应措施。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## Phase 2: 深度分析\n\n🚨 **紧急情况！系统处于危险状态（5.0/10）**\n\n发现严重问题：\n- **PAT-038**: Gateway 内存泄漏 - 1.84GB (50.1%)\n- **PAT-039**: 系统内存紧张 - 仅 164MB 可用\n- 增长率: 175MB/小时\n- 无 Swap 缓冲\n\n## Phase 3: 主动改进\n\n### C. 创建紧急内存释放脚本"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_40d4445a551348b6a9f60435","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/emergency-memory-free.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# emergency-memory-free.sh - 紧急内存释放脚本\n# 创建时间: 2026-02-27 20:30 (Round 250)\n# 用途: 紧急情况下释放内存，防止 OOM\n\nset -euo pipefail\n\n# 颜色定义\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nBLUE='\\033[0;34m'\nNC='\\033[0m'\n\n# 阈值\nCRITICAL_MEM_MB=200\nWARN_MEM_MB=500\n\necho \"=========================================\"\necho \"🚨 紧急内存释放工具\"\necho \"时间: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\"\necho \"=========================================\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 获取当前内存状态\nMEM_AVAIL=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $7}')\nMEM_TOTAL=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $2}')\nMEM_USED_PERCENT=$((100 - (MEM_AVAIL * 100 / MEM_TOTAL)))\n\necho -e \"${BLUE}当前内存状态:${NC}\"\necho \"  总内存: ${MEM_TOTAL}MB\"\necho \"  可用内存: ${MEM_AVAIL}MB\"\necho \"  使用率: ${MEM_USED_PERCENT}%\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 检查是否需要紧急处理\nif [[ $MEM_AVAIL -lt $CRITICAL_MEM_MB ]]; then\n  echo -e \"${RED}🚨 危险: 可用内存 < ${CRITICAL_MEM_MB}MB${NC}\"\n  EMERGENCY=true\nelif [[ $MEM_AVAIL -lt $WARN_MEM_MB ]]; then\n  echo -e \"${YELLOW}⚠️  警告: 可用内存 < ${WARN_MEM_MB}MB${NC}\"\n  EMERGENCY=true\nelse\n  echo -e \"${GREEN}✅ 内存状态正常${NC}\"\n  EMERGENCY=false\nfi\n\necho \"\"\n\nif [[ \"$EMERGENCY\" == \"true\" ]]; then\n  echo -e \"${YELLOW}开始紧急内存释放...${NC}\"\n  echo \"\"\n\n  # 1. 清理 PageCache\n  echo \"1. 清理 PageCache...\"\n  sync && echo 1 > /proc/sys/vm/drop_caches 2>/dev/null || {\n    echo -e \"${YELLOW}需要 root 权限清理缓存${NC}\"\n  }\n  sleep 1\n\n  # 2. 清理 dentries 和 inodes\n  echo \"2. 清理 dentries 和 inodes...\"\n  sync && echo 2 > /proc/sys/vm/drop_caches 2>/dev/null || true\n  sleep 1\n\n  # 3. 清理所有缓存\n  echo \"3. 清理所有缓存...\"\n  sync && echo 3 > /proc/sys/vm/drop_caches 2>/dev/null || true\n  sleep 1\n\n  # 4. 压缩内存\n  echo \"4. 触发内存压缩...\"\n  echo 1 > /proc/sys/vm/compact_memory 2>/dev/null || true\n\n  echo \"\"\n  echo -e \"${GREEN}✅ 紧急释放完成${NC}\"\n  echo \"\"\n\n  # 重新检查内存\n  MEM_AVAIL_NEW=$(free -m | awk '/Mem:/ {print $7}')\n  MEM_FREED=$((MEM_AVAIL_NEW - MEM_AVAIL))\n\n  echo \"释放结果:\"\n  echo \"  之前: ${MEM_AVAIL}MB\"\n  echo \"  之后: ${MEM_AVAIL_NEW}MB\"\n  echo \"  释放: ${MEM_FREED}MB\"\n  echo \"\"\n\n  # Gateway 建议\n  GATEWAY_MEM=$(ps aux | grep \"openclaw-gateway\" | grep -v grep | awk '{print int($6/1024)}')\n\n  if [[ -n \"$GATEWAY_MEM\" ]]; then\n    echo -e \"${YELLOW}Gateway 内存: ${GATEWAY_MEM}MB${NC}\"\n\n    if [[ $GATEWAY_MEM -gt 1500 ]]; then\n      echo \"\"\n      echo -e \"${RED}⚠️  Gateway 内存使用过高 (> 1.5GB)${NC}\"\n      echo -e \"${YELLOW}建议立即重启 Gateway:${NC}\"\n      echo \"  openclaw gateway restart\"\n      echo \"\"\n      echo -e \"${YELLOW}或在低峰期自动重启（今晚 03:00）:${NC}\"\n      echo \"  echo '0 3 * * * openclaw gateway restart' | crontab -\"\n    fi\n  fi\n\n  # Swap 建议\n  SWAP_TOTAL=$(free -m | awk '/Swap:/ {print $2}')\n\n  if [[ $SWAP_TOTAL -eq 0 ]]; then\n    echo \"\"\n    echo -e \"${RED}⚠️  未配置 Swap${NC}\"\n    echo -e \"${YELLOW}建议配置 2GB Swap:${NC}\"\n    echo \"  sudo fallocate -l 2G /swapfile\"\n    echo \"  sudo chmod 600 /swapfile\"\n    echo \"  sudo mkswap /swapfile\"\n    echo \"  sudo swapon /swapfile\"\n    echo \"  echo '/swapfile none swap sw 0 0' | sudo tee -a /etc/fstab\"\n  fi\n\nelse\n  echo \"无需紧急处理\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=========================================\"\n\n# 返回可用内存（MB）\necho $MEM_AVAIL\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7a33e00e7e6f4f01b356bce1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod +x /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/emergency-memory-free.sh"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5ee951efbd674c4584496cd2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/emergency-memory-free.sh 2>&1 | head -50"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2125,"output":1531,"cacheRead":106944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110600,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772195432900}}
