{"type":"message","id":"c6625261","parentId":"a841810c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T16:31:56.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，SSH 攻击防护脚本已创建并运行，封禁了 1 个 IP（159.89.117.252）。\n\n现在让我更新系统健康检查脚本，增加 SSH 攻击检测功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"### B. 改进系统健康检查脚本"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_42a21e1317414d0ba429e493","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/system-health-check.sh","oldText":"### 模块 4: 维护状态\ncheck_maintenance() {\n  log \"🔧 检查维护状态...\"\n  echo \"\"\n\n  # 检查最近的清理记录\n  LAST_CLEANUP=$(find /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory -name \"disk-cleanup-report-*.md\" -mtime -1 2>/dev/null | head -1)\n\n  if [[ -n \"$LAST_CLEANUP\" ]]; then\n    log_success \"最近清理: $(basename $LAST_CLEANUP)\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 5))\n  else\n    log_info \"最近清理: > 24 小时前\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 2))\n  fi\n\n  # 检查旧日志数量\n  OLD_LOGS=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mtime +7 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\n\n  log \"  超过 7 天的日志: ${OLD_LOGS} 个\"\n\n  if [[ $OLD_LOGS -eq 0 ]]; then\n    log_success \"日志管理: 优秀\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 5))\n  elif [[ $OLD_LOGS -lt 10 ]]; then\n    log_info \"日志管理: 良好\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 3))\n  else\n    log_warning \"日志管理: 需要清理\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 1))\n  fi\n\n  # 计算维护评分 (满分 10)\n  MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE * 10 / 10))\n  log \"  维护模块评分: ${MAINTENANCE_SCORE}/10\"\n  echo \"\"\n}","newText":"### 模块 4: 维护状态\ncheck_maintenance() {\n  log \"🔧 检查维护状态...\"\n  echo \"\"\n\n  # 检查最近的清理记录\n  LAST_CLEANUP=$(find /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory -name \"disk-cleanup-report-*.md\" -mtime -1 2>/dev/null | head -1)\n\n  if [[ -n \"$LAST_CLEANUP\" ]]; then\n    log_success \"最近清理: $(basename $LAST_CLEANUP)\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 5))\n  else\n    log_info \"最近清理: > 24 小时前\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 2))\n  fi\n\n  # 检查旧日志数量\n  OLD_LOGS=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -mtime +7 2>/dev/null | wc -l || echo 0)\n\n  log \"  超过 7 天的日志: ${OLD_LOGS} 个\"\n\n  if [[ $OLD_LOGS -eq 0 ]]; then\n    log_success \"日志管理: 优秀\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 5))\n  elif [[ $OLD_LOGS -lt 10 ]]; then\n    log_info \"日志管理: 良好\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 3))\n  else\n    log_warning \"日志管理: 需要清理\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 1))\n  fi\n\n  # SSH 攻击检测 (Round 251 新增)\n  SSH_ATTACKS=$(journalctl -u sshd --since \"6 hours ago\" 2>/dev/null | \\\n    grep -E \"Invalid user|Failed password|Connection closed\" | wc -l || echo 0)\n\n  log \"  SSH 攻击 (6h): ${SSH_ATTACKS} 次\"\n\n  if [[ $SSH_ATTACKS -eq 0 ]]; then\n    log_success \"SSH 安全: 优秀\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 5))\n  elif [[ $SSH_ATTACKS -lt 10 ]]; then\n    log_info \"SSH 安全: 良好\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 3))\n  elif [[ $SSH_ATTACKS -lt 50 ]]; then\n    log_warning \"SSH 安全: 有攻击 (${SSH_ATTACKS} 次)\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE + 1))\n  else\n    log_error \"SSH 安全: 严重攻击 (${SSH_ATTACKS} 次)\"\n    MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE - 2))\n  fi\n\n  # 计算维护评分 (满分 10)\n  MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE * 10 / 15))\n  MAINTENANCE_SCORE=$((MAINTENANCE_SCORE > 10 ? 10 : MAINTENANCE_SCORE))\n  log \"  维护模块评分: ${MAINTENANCE_SCORE}/10\"\n  echo \"\"\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2427,"output":1169,"cacheRead":121728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772209885492}}
